// 3.agr apnko koi kaam ko loop meh n times krna hai , then vaha pe don't use for-loop , simply use while-loop as like this: as mtlb phle apn ek int define kr lenge with the value ki apnko loop ko kitne baar chalana hai, as like int t = 10; and then apn simply while-loop ka use krenge as like this: while(a--) , thus toh esseh apna loop "a" times hi chalega mtlb 10-times hi chalega.

